ass=\"text-sm text-stone truncate mb-2\" style=\"line-height: 20px;\">22-week ultrasound scan</p>\n256\t                  <span class=\"badge-pill bg-mint/20 text-graphite\">Next: Jun 12</span>\n257\t                </div>\n258\t                <span class=\"text-xs text-stone shrink-0 ml-2\">11:30 AM</span>\n259\t              </div>\n260\t            </div>\n261\t\n262\t          </div>\n263\t\n264\t        </section>\n265\t\n266\t      </main>\n267\t\n268\t      <!-- FAB - Add new entry -->\n269\t      <button data-flutter=\"fab\" class=\"animate-fab fab-tap absolute bottom-6 right-4 w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-lavender shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center\">\n270\t        <svg class=\"w-7 h-7 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n271\t          <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" d=\"M12 4v16m8-8H4\"/>\n272\t        </svg>\n273\t      </button>\n274\t\n275\t    </div>\n276\t  </div>\n277\t</body>\n278\t</html>"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4c2d248f-6ca9-438c-a739-04b7700593a1","uuid":"2e8827dc-14e8-4c58-9229-2ccebf13514e","timestamp":"2026-05-19T01:01:35.933Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/designs/health-log/design.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=375, initial-scale=1.0\">\n  <title>Health Log — Baby Bump Design</title>\n  <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n  <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n  <script>\n    tailwind.config = {\n      theme: {\n        extend: {\n          colors: {\n            'lavender': '#7C3AED',\n            'lavender-tint': '#F5F3FF',\n            'blush': '#F9A8D4',\n            'mint': '#6EE7B7',\n            'mist': '#FAFAFA',\n            'graphite': '#1F2937',\n            'stone': '#6B7280',\n            'misty-border': '#E5E7EB',\n            'coral': '#EF4444',\n            'warm-white': '#FFFFFF',\n          },\n          fontFamily: {\n            'nunito': ['Nunito', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],\n          },\n          borderRadius: {\n            'card': '16px',\n            'sheet': '28px',\n            'pill': '999px',\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  </script>\n  <style>\n    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n    body {\n      font-family: 'Nunito', system-ui, sans-serif;\n      background: #E8E8E8;\n      display: flex;\n      justify-content: center;\n      padding: 32px 16px;\n      min-height: 100vh;\n    }\n    .phone {\n      width: 375px;\n      min-height: 812px;\n      border-radius: 40px;\n      overflow: hidden;\n      position: relative;\n      box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n    }\n    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {\n      *, *::before, *::after {\n        animation-duration: 0.01ms !important;\n        transition-duration: 0.01ms !important;\n      }\n    }\n    .card-shadow {\n      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n    }\n    .entry-tap:active {\n      transform: scale(0.98);\n      transition: transform 200ms ease-out;\n    }\n    .fab-tap:active {\n      transform: scale(0.90);\n      transition: transform 200ms ease-out;\n    }\n    .badge-pill {\n      padding: 4px 10px;\n      border-radius: 999px;\n      font-size: 11px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n    }\n    .severity-dot {\n      width: 8px;\n      height: 8px;\n      border-radius: 999px;\n    }\n    @keyframes fade-in {\n      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }\n      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }\n    }\n    .animate-fade-in {\n      animation: fade-in 300ms ease-out backwards;\n    }\n    @keyframes fab-appear {\n      from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.95); }\n      to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }\n    }\n    .animate-fab {\n      animation: fab-appear 200ms ease-out backwards;\n      animation-delay: 300ms;\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"phone\">\n\n    <!-- Scaffold -->\n    <div data-flutter=\"scaffold\" class=\"scaffold flex flex-col min-h-screen bg-lavender-tint\">\n\n      <!-- AppBar -->\n      <header data-flutter=\"app-bar\" class=\"flex items-center h-14 px-4 bg-lavender-tint\">\n        <button data-flutter=\"icon-btn\" aria-label=\"Go back\" class=\"w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full hover:bg-lavender/10\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-graphite\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n            <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 19l-7-7 7-7\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </button>\n        <h1 class=\"flex-1 text-xl font-semibold text-graphite text-center pr-12\">Health Log</h1>\n        <button data-flutter=\"icon-btn\" aria-label=\"Filter entries\" class=\"w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full hover:bg-lavender/10\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6 text-graphite\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n            <path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h16a1 1 0 011 1v2.586a1 1 0 01-.293.707l-6.414 6.414a1 1 0 00-.293.707V17l-4 4v-6.586a1 1 0 00-.293-.707L3.293 7.293A1 1 0 013 6.586V4z\"/>\n          </svg>\n        </button>\n      </header>\n\n      <!-- Body - ListView with sections -->\n      <main data-flutter=\"custom-scroll\" class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto px-4 pb-24\">\n\n        <!-- Section 1: Summary Stats Banner -->\n        <section class=\"mt-6 mb-6 animate-fade-in\" style=\"animation-delay: 0ms;\">\n          <div data-flutter=\"card\" class=\"bg-mist rounded-card card-shadow p-4\">\n            <div data-flutter=\"row\" data-main-axis=\"space-between\" class=\"flex justify-between